title: Sunny 2bdrm in Victorian Red Brick Rowhouse, Great Location!
posting_body: ['Sunny Lakeview/Roscoe Village 2-bedroom apartment in a lovely 6 Unit red Victorian Rowhouse with high ceilings, private deck, hardwood floors, and eat-in kitchen w/ dishwasher, in a stunning vintage Victorian Red Brick Rowhouse!', ' Walk to all your favorite Wrigleyville area shops and restaurants!', 'Apartment Features:', '* Central Heat and AC', '*', 'Large living Room', '* 2 large queen-size bedrooms with ample closet space', '* Bright eat-in kitchen', '* Lots of kitchen cabinets and counter space', '* Pantry', '* Hardwood floors and natural original woodwork throughout', 'Building Features:', '* NO PETS, nonsmokers', '* Rear deck', '* Common area patio', '* Laundry room with three washers and three dryers', '* Free storage locker', '* Good zoned street parking', 'Neighborhood Features:', "* WALKSCORE 89% - Walker's Paradise!", '* 3 blocks West of Southport for shops and restaurants', '* 1 block to Paulina Brown Line "L" stop.', "* One block east to Starbucks, restaurants, nightlife, and shopping on Lincoln Avenue -- Whole Foods, Trader Joe's, and  Target within walking distance.", 'We have been in business since 1968 and do business as Central City Management.', 'We are family-owned and managed and care about our tenants and their apartment homes.', "You are encouraged to view current and former tenants' ratings on Yelp and Google."]
